    <h2>📊 Sharpe Ratio Calculator</h2>
    <p style="color:#9aa0a6;margin-bottom:1.2rem;">Enter your portfolio's return, the risk-free rate, and standard deviation to calculate the Sharpe ratio and see how well your risk is being compensated.</p>
